{{/usCountry}}
{{^usCountry}}
Meteorologists said the current conditions resemble prolonged pre-monsoon heat episodes, with heat stress increasing significantly during afternoon hours. The absence of cloud cover and rainfall has further aggravated conditions.
{{/usCountry}}
{{#usCountry}}
